equipment for educational institutions, the expansion and 
outfitting of regional directorates, lycee construction, cadre 
training, the purchase of land, the establishment of new schools 
and university residence halls, the replacement and acquisition 
of equipment for university social programs, and so on. 
  Those projects have a budget totaling D115.917 million. 
  2. Financial operations: D3.83 million. 


