<H3> <TI>   Ukraine Transfers Nuclear Warheads to Russia Amid Fuel Controversy </TI></H3>
<H4>   Kravchuk Announces Removal While in Washington </H4>
<F P=102> LD0503081594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0528 GMT 5 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0503081594 </F>
