Article   Type:BFN 

  [Editorial Report] Tel Aviv HA'ARETZ in Hebrew on 25 
February, in a page A9 reported by ITIM, states: "Two heroin 
smugglers from the Galilee village of Julis, Daniyel 'Amad 
Mukhtar, 25, and 'Amad Nayif Hasan, 30, were sentenced by the 
Haifa District court to six years imprisonment after being 
convicted of smuggling 2 kg of heroin from Lebanon to Israel. 
They were apprehended by the police in May 1993 

</TEXT>

